# 🎓 SGSN-CMC — Système de Gestion Scolaire Numérique

[![Azure](https://img.shields.io/badge/Azure-VM-blue)](https://azure.microsoft.com)
[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-✓-blue)](https://docker.com)
[![Node.js](https://img.shields.io/badge/Node.js-20-green)](https://nodejs.org)
[![PostgreSQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/PostgreSQL-16-blue)](https://postgresql.org)

> Projet de fin d'études — Filière Infrastructure Digitale (Cloud Computing)  
> Centre de Formation CMC Nouaceur — 2026

## 🌐 Live Demo
**🔗 http://sgsncmc.duckdns.org**  
**📚 API Docs: http://sgsncmc.duckdns.org/api-docs**

## ✨ Features

- 🔐 **Authentication multi-rôles** (Admin, Gestionnaire, Professeur, Étudiant)
- 📊 **CRUD Complet** (Stagiaires, Notes, Absences, Emploi du temps)
- 🐳 **Docker Containerized** (Full stack with Docker Compose)
- ☁️ **Cloud Deployed** (Azure VM + Ubuntu 24.04)
- 📖 **API Documentation** (Swagger/OpenAPI 3.0)
- 🎨 **Responsive UI** (Tailwind CSS + Glassmorphism design)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | HTML5, Tailwind CSS, Vanilla JS |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL 16 |
| **DevOps** | Docker, Docker Compose |
| **Cloud** | Azure Virtual Machine |
| **Docs** | Swagger UI |

